{"tid":1053922,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[T寶]周子瑜說日文網友暴動啦　忘詞靠團友SANA救援","createTime":"2019-03-09T12:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T10:49:01.000Z","uid":46435,"like":16,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe59ad7626ef727b9c12c104f116191307c6e07","tid":1053922,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣女團「TWICE」推出第2張日文專輯《TWICE2》，8成員獲邀到朝日電視台音樂節目《MUSIC STATION》作客。昨晚播出以畢業為主題，主持人塔摩利詢問成員畢業的回憶，來自中國台灣的周子瑜難得秀日文說：「我畢業典禮沒有哭過，但是去韓國的時候&hellip;」講到一半突然忘詞，仍盡力想著準備好的日文一字一句回答，日本成員SANA在一旁幫忙提詞，子瑜說日文的模樣在日本推特上獲網友大讚，直呼：「努力說日文的子瑜真的太可愛了！」<br />\n<br />\n周子瑜在成員的幫助下說出自己的回憶：「去韓國的時候想到要跟好朋友分開，就大哭了。」說完日文的她害羞倒向MINA身上，其他成員笑開懷為她鼓掌。周子瑜小學畢業照也同時公開，引來日本網友熱烈討論：「從小就超美！」也有許多粉絲讚她日、韓兩地跑，說的都不是母語，「一定花了很多心思準備」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFmBpAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFmBpAY.jpg&h=22cd86ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜受訪時透露自己在畢業典禮的時候從來沒哭過。翻攝朝日電視台畫面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ummat2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fummat2R.jpg&h=bd6ccec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周子瑜難得用日文回答，緊張地頻看下方。翻攝朝日電視台畫面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PSzCTxW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPSzCTxW.gif&h=8a970ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萌萌噠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來自中國的小姐姐就只服周子和怡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd97b86ebcf9d6b966854831fc9764a38e99b62","tid":1053922,"uid":63057,"like":20,"dislike":44,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"怡人完勝支瑜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbR0khS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbR0khS.jpg&h=a14e2e6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca00b0b7b02e5a356204d42ce7a16f38f3cf8b6f","tid":1053922,"uid":56701,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"樓主咁後生可能唔多明<br />\n支那只得雞,台灣先有女神<br />\n唔好混埋一齊講,你睇程潚而家已經變返做咩?"},{"pid":"c42ec5f8b2f0a6452b4cb8ddefaf9858f177ec21","tid":1053922,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8bd97b86ebcf9d6b966854831fc9764a38e99b62","tid":1053922,"uid":63057,"like":20,"dislike":44,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"怡人完勝支瑜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbR0khS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbR0khS.jpg&h=a14e2e6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"兩個小姐姐都靚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd68f609baadda67b7eb20d9136d1f954b1f4f5","tid":1053922,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:53:40.000Z","msg":"好可愛"},{"pid":"1ddd5e5f5965b3f8546d66a9e781e32b15f43ad5","tid":1053922,"uid":198831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"點解台灣新聞發生親啲咩都話暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4da3f87c602d87f83c3a1a25d86fa7e6ecd355e","tid":1053922,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca00b0b7b02e5a356204d42ce7a16f38f3cf8b6f","tid":1053922,"uid":56701,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:10:27.000Z","msg":"樓主咁後生可能唔多明<br />\n支那只得雞,台灣先有女神<br />\n唔好混埋一齊講,你睇程潚而家已經變返做咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07698a66f13a8dc673c0614f717ad6800d01fb75","tid":1053922,"uid":46435,"like":3,"dislike